These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
2 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, biathlon
1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | pony |
| Sport   | biathlon     | snowboarding  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, entrepreneur
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, orchid
1. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Job         | entrepreneur   | librarian      |
| Flower   | marigold | orchid |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, grapefruit
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, superhero
1. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Food   | grapefruit | pepper    |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | indonesian |
| Birthday   | july | march |

