.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, snooker
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, blend
1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Game   | snooker | scrabble |
| Cigar     | blend    | alhambra    |

